/*
!.gitignore

# Dependency: libdatachannel
!libdatachannel
libdatachannel/*
!libdatachannel/include
!libdatachannel/src
!libdatachannel/test
libdatachannel/test/*
!libdatachannel/test/*.cpp
!libdatachannel/test/*.hpp
!libdatachannel/LICENSE
!libdatachannel/Makefile
!libdatachannel/CMakeLists.txt

# Dependency: mbedtls generated files - https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls/blob/v3.6.5/library/.gitignore#L5-L11
# 
# NOTE(jae): 2026-03-13
# We provide these so that mbedtls can easily switched to use a fork for bug-fixes.
# ie. https://github.com/paullouisageneau/libdatachannel/issues/1520
!mbedtls-gen

# Dependency: openssl generated files - https://github.com/kassane/openssl-zig/tree/zig-pkg/include_gen
!openssl-gen
